{"tid":1467969,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［核爆都唔割蓆］813機場賽後檢討！香港人必勝！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:17:48.000Z","uid":217306,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f10de39fcfa5012d3072bc7767a4c10d96e97256","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核爆都唔割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講得兄弟爬山自然就當大家係手足<br />\n<br />\n其實係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全世界眼中我哋任何一個人都代表着呢個群體</span></span>，就好似任何一隻警犬都代表左整個香港警察。<br />\n<br />\n手足做錯左，我哋就要大家一齊諗解決嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我建議以下三大方向：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 喺民間記者會度<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為所有造成嘅不便以及所有有機會失民心嘅地方作出誠懇道歉</span></span>，並且解釋背後動機原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">制定一套規矩然後自己規管自己</span></span>。呢度冇人需要大台因為每個人都係大台，所以要記得你着起嗰一身衫，出現喺嗰個地方你就代表着整個群體。<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當我地有一啲軍規係廣泛認同並且大家一齊遵守嘅時候，我哋根本唔需要搵邊個係鬼因為其他傳媒全世界嘅人都會分辨到</span></span>。記唔記得616分紅海啊？<br />\n<br />\n而為咗全世界都分辨到嘅話，我哋討論之後如果大家主流都同意，就應該要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">由民間記者會對外公布我哋有咁嘅規矩，令公眾得以知情。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 抗爭分工，做好多元化抗爭路線。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">令到外國真正會出手幫我地，要令全世界知：係中共得米之後你哋會點樣跟住我哋一齊仆街。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果冇任何利害關係，所有外國嘅國家以及傳媒睇香港都只會係睇第二個敘利亞咁，我哋越用私刑，世界就越唔清楚我哋同警察嘅分別，就越加快成為第二個敘利亞。所以我哋要保持住我哋絕對嘅優勢，點樣係贏盡全世界掌聲之餘話比大家知：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">If we burn,you burn with us😡 抗爭輸咗，唔單止係中共要同我地一齊落地獄，而係全世界都要同我地一齊落地獄。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好令到811爆左隻眼嘅女仔白白失去左隻眼<br />\n我哋用智慧，以眼還眼<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人必勝！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3f683f46cad389768855cc550bca3d194942566a","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"6eab2e0964f53f1c66472a9ceac06f70c1f9a9a6","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5f1ebebf708a9ddc3a4e6d28af2694cd05fd85b","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c29db294bba0c808464e1237813d9d93654849e6","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd039f14ca6d4e5cb12386dd49cf9f2d638f01ac","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6104e4f96dc534c19f29275c1c2564497225f9ec","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33e2a5a665ee072a7702c267659508d822f6f0ca","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7ee80023447c5c244776f147fd488212fe455dc","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f14b3e7499c72d27d80e2b9fa9ff3be1f9678719","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0ed191563db0bd6b3993a0e6c8b1d0738a3eaf7","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7015e4673b49901a286f3cf62b1344d9c732228c","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf1da6f51e91eb8e41b27b5263a4bf6f4d5d447c","tid":1467969,"uid":232575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:27.000Z","msg":"小弟愚見:<br />\n<br />\n沙田、黃大仙、將軍奧令大軍迷糊了思想<br />\n<br />\n之前多區的週未運動使大軍相信自己大勝利。接二連三既大勝利令到大軍雄心壯志。相信同樣模式行下去便能走向勝利。依種信心聚集了人群，但過度的信心卻使大軍開始貪心。直擊心臟--機場。<br />\n<br />\n地區<br />\n要知道<span style=\"color: red;\">地區勝利在於天時、地利、人和</span>，各區各自有強大的區民BACK UP。1天時:週未運動至少有一星期策劃人員。2地利:前線撑握百分百地理知識、地區NPC居民伸手幫助。3人和:地區由黃色區民組成。<br />\n<br />\n機場<br />\n由爆眼、到計畫、到佔領、到取消反航班不足24小時，根本無計畫的共識。最「錯(失誤)」既係用太短時間掫合「走派」、「留派」一同佔領機場<br />\n<br />\n機場無本地區民，來往機場的不是香港人為主，加上商業因素與不合作示威背道而馳"},{"pid":"73b59b4275e7e69a2dba21b45ca1f34b059d73b5","tid":1467969,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a522fe868254ce51feb7f663a0884028b527f765","tid":1467969,"uid":154557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"補鑊方法必推"},{"pid":"6707ec8d291c6f916d486855268fe10e65691f80","tid":1467969,"uid":54186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:39.000Z","msg":"推左先講<br />\n唔割蓆  繼續各有各做<br />\n要有自我約束   就唔會有同類事件<br />\n就可以贏！"},{"pid":"2424a0fe5207acad911d0744fb0b72e6ba1420af","tid":1467969,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:38.000Z","msg":"（建議）而家要點樣補救/澄清示威者打記者/救護？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467741</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想幫你推奈何p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人愚見<br />\n絕對唔可以一開波就話係鬼做<br />\n就算係真<br />\n都會俾人感覺你冇反省自己<br />\n只係推卸責任"},{"pid":"816cdd22cc4115783e403dc82d7c8558e53b3412","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86c005052d6aab73e0bcfb40314dda1077c0e6af","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7d9553a462460f92a4e9676e24fcab76c727842","tid":1467969,"uid":228244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"懇請勇武派勇士冷靜勿被挑釁，請明白，頭先阻住救護救人嗰批，如果我哋阻住人道救援，又有乜資格呼籲國際聲援甚至通過香港人權法呢，所以守住除自衞外武力不用於人係咁重要，輿論一輸抗爭本錢基乎就少咗一大半。<br />\n<br />\n好似罷工咁，你可呼籲但不能強制別人罷工，喺機場既旅客各有自己故事，唔係個個出嚟遊埠散心，有啲可能工幹完歸心似箭，有啲甚至要見親人最後一面，示威者可爭取市民和旅客的諒解與支持，但係唔應該將自己訴求凌駕於別人既需求，咁做最終只會輸輿論壞大事。<br />\n<br />\n聽日環時必定大造文章，國務院發言譴責，成功煽動十四億人民仇港，阻醫護救人時外國傳媒全程影住，香港抗爭者在佢哋眼中隨時已逆轉成暴徒，輿論一輸我哋抗爭本錢就少一大半，所以請勇武派切記要冷靜，除自衞外不能對人使用武力或阻人救援，否則只會把文宣組的努力白費。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者只能塞爆機場間接令機管局自我癱瘓，但絕不能主動阻旅客登機，人道救援更不可作出任何阻撓。<br />\n<br />\n現在大家只能見步行步..."},{"pid":"f25c0a1d6ce2a8b642f3ddae080347a8b7c9e24b","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2424a0fe5207acad911d0744fb0b72e6ba1420af","tid":1467969,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:38.000Z","msg":"（建議）而家要點樣補救/澄清示威者打記者/救護？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467741</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想幫你推奈何p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人愚見<br />\n絕對唔可以一開波就話係鬼做<br />\n就算係真<br />\n都會俾人感覺你冇反省自己<br />\n只係推卸責任"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:02.000Z","msg":"啱啊<br />\n我哋唔可以同啲狗一樣推卸責任<br />\n做錯就一定要認"},{"pid":"e2ade356ec105ce25c49a6e2a064699e7636c4e7","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4371a5787caf2ec52ed09d14cfd5aae77b94ad3","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9095bbe9a42a12892d0963c8ca441cdc421fe66","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bcfc75c097e0c83bd7a3b9446ced180cf8da2ad","tid":1467969,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f25c0a1d6ce2a8b642f3ddae080347a8b7c9e24b","tid":1467969,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2424a0fe5207acad911d0744fb0b72e6ba1420af","tid":1467969,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0